  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger, sauté for 1-2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add toasted and ground Sichuan peppercorns, cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add diced Canary melon, cook for 3-4 minutes until lightly browned.",
    "Add chopped scallions, cook for an additional 1-2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Stir in chopped fresh cilantro and lime juice.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
